OL,6,F"That means we can recycle that money
OL,7,Fto then go back to helping the next
OL,8,Fgeneration of people. So it's
OL,9,Fsustainable."
OL,11,FThe support would only be for first-
OL,12,Ftime buyers and could cover up to 40%
OL,13,Fof the cost of a property. It would
OL,14,Fnot apply to new builds but secondary
OL,15,Fmarket homes only.
